RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2001-0960. Westside Cellular, Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 93-1758-RC-CSS. Reported at 98 Ohio St.3d 165, 2002-Ohio-7119, 781 N.E.2d 199. On motion for reconsideration of Cincinnati SMSA Limited Partnership and motion for reconsideration. Motions denied.

Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., dissent. Resnick, J., not participating.
